{"tid":2514274,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"袁國勇：籲打疫苗 檢測成本高昂 香港還有多少儲備可以花費下去？","createTime":"2021-05-03T07:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T07:46:12.000Z","uid":21470,"like":15,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":117,"replies":[{"pid":"f9653d17144648f96cbe6959e0243f3036113a06","tid":2514274,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:04:25.000Z","msg":"袁國勇籲打疫苗 「香港有多少儲備可以花費下去？」<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇強調，接種疫苗是暫時唯一令大家重回正常生活的方法，除了病情控制欠佳的長期病患者，或者對疫苗成份有敏感反應的人士之外，其他人都應該考慮接種疫苗。他形容本港得天獨厚，死亡個案比英美等地少，但指病毒檢測成本高昂，反問香港有多少財政儲備可以花費下去，認為市民不應再浪費時間、持續觀望。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389915\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2389915&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOGipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=50b1e8f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389915</a>"},{"pid":"1b4a00e5fc1d5ebf59404b1991d5604e18970b54","tid":2514274,"uid":77196,"like":107,"dislike":1,"score":106,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:05:13.000Z","msg":"唔填海咪大撚把囉，仲有CUT埋果班忠誠廢物仲多呀"},{"pid":"ea9b935be0a10716fe848370a75e22f73f515a09","tid":2514274,"uid":36287,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:05:14.000Z","msg":"好撚多...?"},{"pid":"d8d098726bf6a47e1e3f396612ce88d716b71bc3","tid":2514274,"uid":263780,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:06:11.000Z","msg":"唔好比我地檢測囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938e87b627cd71f03fdec03af55f94b7680545de","tid":2514274,"uid":14918,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:06:52.000Z","msg":"不了, no stake in society"},{"pid":"953205d939849152e9a2b979d07dce9a69c59288","tid":2514274,"uid":62226,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:07:31.000Z","msg":"我已經唔記得咩係正常生活<br />\n正常生活